'''詹森·洛維'''（{{lang-en|Jason Lowe}}；{{bd|1991年|9月2日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場，但也可以勝任右後衛。他現在效力於[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽]]球隊[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aberdeen/9379180.stm |title=Blackburn injuries halt Jason Lowe's move to Aberdeen |author=Liam McLeod |date=31 January 2011 |work=BBC Sport |accessdate=28 October 2011 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613141209/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aberdeen/9379180.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也曾代表英格蘭青年隊參賽。

==球會生涯==
===布萊克本流浪者===
賈森·洛加入[[布萊克本流浪者足球俱樂部|布萊克本流浪者]]時為U12球員，在2009年9月4日簽下首份職業合約後提拔至預備隊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rovers.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10303~1787566,00.html |title=Duo pen pro deals |date=4 September 2009 |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |accessdate=28 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090907073204/http://www.rovers.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10303~1787566,00.html |archivedate=2009-09-07 }}</ref>。2011年1月8日[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]對[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者]]，上演他的職業處子秀<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rovers.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10303~54887,00.html |title=Blackburn 1–0 QPR |date=8 January 2011 |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |accessdate=28 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111014225535/http://www.rovers.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0%2C%2C10303~54887%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-10-14 }}</ref>。一星期後對[[車路士|車路士]]的比賽，他首次在[[英超|英超]]職業登場，在24分鐘入替受傷的[[大卫·邓恩|大卫·邓恩]]。

3月24日，他被外借至[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[奥尔德姆足球俱乐部|奥尔德姆]]至季末，以獲取比賽經驗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/o/oldham_athletic/9435313.stm |title=Oldham Athletic land Jason Lowe on loan from Blackburn |publisher=BBC Sport |date=24 March 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2017 }}<br>{{cite web |url=http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~2323506,00.html |title=Lowe down on Latics' new boy |publisher=Oldham Athletic A.F.C. |date=24 March 2011 |accessdate=26 March 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110326044534/http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0%2C%2C10337~2323506%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-03-26 }}</ref>。四天後對[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|特兰米尔流浪者]]比賽中首次代表奥尔德姆上場<ref name=sb1011>{{soccerbase season|58118|2010|accessdate=30 August 2017}}</ref>，4月3日2-0擊敗[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]一戰中主射[[點球|點球]]，打進他個人在球會首顆進球<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~2329485,00.html |title=Second-half report |publisher=Oldham Athletic A.F.C. |date=3 April 2011 |accessdate=28 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405200806/http://www.oldhamathletic.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0%2C%2C10337~2329485%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-04-05 }}</ref>，4月25日對[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|沃尔索尔]]打進在球會第二顆進球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13112141.stm |title=Oldham 1–1 Walsall |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 April 2011 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2011-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428005059/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13112141.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整個外借期間他共上場7次射入2球<ref name=sb1011/>。

賈森·洛在布萊克本流浪者下次上場是2011年8月24日[[英格蘭足球聯賽盃|英格蘭足球聯賽盃]]對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|谢周三]]一戰<ref name=sb1112>{{soccerbase season|58118|2011|accessdate=30 August 2017}}</ref>。9月11日對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富勒姆]]，是他在新球季首次聯賽上場<ref name=sb1112/>。9月11日對[[阿森納|阿森納]]首次先發上場，六天之後他與球會簽下五年長約<ref name=5YearDeal>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15481937.stm |title=Jason Lowe agrees five-year Blackburn Rovers deal |publisher=BBC Sport |date=27 October 2011 |accessdate=28 October 2011 |archive-date=2011-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111105205111/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15481937.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後他繼續是球隊常規上場成員之一，司職不同位置，整個球季他在各項比賽共上場37次<ref name=sb1112/><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/17973169 |title=Chelsea 2–1 Blackburn |first=Owen |last=Phillips |publisher=BBC Sport |date=13 May 2012 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627084846/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/17973169 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012/13球季，賈森·洛隨球會降級至英冠作賽。他在新球季首次上場是作客[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|伊普斯维奇城]]，司職左邊衛並打進[[烏龍球|烏龍球]]，最終以和局完成賽事<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2015/february/getting-personal-with-jason-lowe/ |title='Getting Personal' with Jason Lowe |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |date=4 February 2015 |accessdate=5 September 2017 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926232831/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2015/february/getting-personal-with-jason-lowe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[看守領隊|看守領隊]][[埃里克·布萊克|埃里克·布萊克]]執教期間，賈森·洛經常司職中場位置<ref name=Soccerway>{{cite web |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/jason-lowe/168862/ |title=J. Lowe |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=13 September 2017 |archive-date=2019-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712230549/https://int.soccerway.com/players/jason-lowe/168862/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。縱使球季經歷多位主教練變動，他仍然在球隊中場穩固自己位置<ref name=Soccerway/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/10134285.Lowe_is_bidding_to_start_2013_in_style_as_turmoil_continues/ |title=Lowe is bidding to start 2013 in style as turmoil continues |first=Andy |last=Cryer |newspaper=The Lancashire Telegraph |date=1 January 2013 |accessdate=5 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613160602/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/10134285.Lowe_is_bidding_to_start_2013_in_style_as_turmoil_continues/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，使他整個球季各項賽事共上場42次。

2013/14球季，他依舊是球隊中場常規成員，在10月更續約至2017年<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/24670838 |title=Jason Lowe: Blackburn midfielder extends contract to 2017 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 October 2013 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405225500/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/24670838 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。四天後對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]賽事，他的25碼射門進球當選為球會球季最佳進球<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24680972 |title=Blackburn Rovers 1–0 Middlesbrough |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2 November 2013 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2013-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105063603/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24680972 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=GoalAim>{{cite news |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11257736.Rovers_ace_Lowe_has_goal_aim/ |title=Rovers ace Lowe has goal aim |newspaper=The Lancashire Telegraph |date=5 June 2014 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613134410/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11257736.Rovers_ace_Lowe_has_goal_aim/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月3日以3-1不敵伊普斯维奇城是他球會第100場比賽<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2013/december/100-not-out-for-lowe/ |title=100 not out for Lowe |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |date=3 December 2013 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613134337/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2013/december/100-not-out-for-lowe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。全季他共上場42次<ref name=sb1314>{{soccerbase season|58118|2013|accessdate=30 August 2017}}</ref>。

2014/15球季，病魔侵擾了賈森·洛。由於球隊缺乏防守球員，使他回到右邊衛位置<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11412014.Jason_Lowe_refuses_to_rule_out_making_right_back_his_long_term_position_for_Blackburn_Rovers/ |title=Jason Lowe refuses to rule out making right back his long-term position for Blackburn Rovers |first=Paul |last=Wheelock |newspaper=The Lancashire Telegraph |date=15 August 2014 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613134244/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11412014.Jason_Lowe_refuses_to_rule_out_making_right_back_his_long_term_position_for_Blackburn_Rovers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。賈森·洛的腳部疲勞性骨折使他退下火線數個月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11472255.TEAM_NEWS__Blackburn_Rovers_v_Wigan_Athletic/ |title=Team news: Blackburn Rovers v Wigan Athletic |first=Paul |last=Wheelock |newspaper=The Lancashire Telegraph |date=13 September 2014 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613134351/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11472255.TEAM_NEWS__Blackburn_Rovers_v_Wigan_Athletic/ |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite news |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11632852.Jason_Lowe_set_to_hand_Blackburn_Rovers_pre_Christmas_fitness_boost/ |title=Jason Lowe set to hand Blackburn Rovers pre-Christmas fitness boost |newspaper=The Lancashire Telegraph |date=28 November 2014 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613134358/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/11632852.Jason_Lowe_set_to_hand_Blackburn_Rovers_pre_Christmas_fitness_boost/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。康復後一星期對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查尔顿竞技]]的比賽，他舊患復發<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2014/december/lowe-concerns/ |title=Lowe concerns |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |date=21 December 2014 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126114522/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2014/december/lowe-concerns/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月中再一次舊傷復發，迫使他進行手術，賈森·洛的賽季提前結束。2015/16球季，他上陣四次後再次受傷<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2015/september/lowe-blow-for-rovers/ |title=Lowe blow for Rovers |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |date=27 September 2015 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128041151/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2015/september/lowe-blow-for-rovers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再度進行手術並休養半年。2016年4月9日對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]一役以先發身份上場,<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36015751 |title=Jason Lowe: Blackburn Rovers return from injury 'felt like debut' |publisher=BBC Sport |date=11 April 2016 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411135621/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36015751 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016/17球季，[[格蘭特·漢利|格蘭特·漢利]]離開球會後，賈森·洛被任命為球隊隊長<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/14652688.Boss_drops_Jason_Lowe_hint_over_vacant_Blackburn_Rovers_captaincy/ |title=Boss drops Jason Lowe hint over vacant Blackburn Rovers captaincy |first=Johnny |last=Greaney |newspaper=The Lancashire Telegraph |date=30 July 2016 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613160525/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/14652688.Boss_drops_Jason_Lowe_hint_over_vacant_Blackburn_Rovers_captaincy/ |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite web |url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2016/september/a-real-honour-for-me/ |title=A real honour for me |publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C. |date=10 September 2016 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303020506/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2016/september/a-real-honour-for-me/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。球隊表現不濟，而他自己亦因累積多張黃牌而停賽。在球季最後一場比賽，縱使布萊克本流浪者以3-1力勝[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|布伦特福德]]，[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]和[[諾丁漢森林足球俱樂部|諾丁漢森林]]各自取勝，使球隊難逃降級命運<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39760414 |title=Brentford 1–3 Blackburn Rovers |publisher=BBC Sport |date=7 May 2017 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013006/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39760414 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。賈森·洛是球會八名季末放棄球員之一<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39962912 |title=Jason Lowe: Blackburn Rovers' captain one of eight released by relegated club |publisher=BBC Sport |date=18 May 2017 |accessdate=12 September 2017 |archive-date=2017-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814164818/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39962912 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
2017年8月31日，他與英冠球會伯明翰簽約一年<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2017/jason-lowe-signs-for-blues/ |title=Jason Lowe signs for Blues |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=31 August 2017 |accessdate=31 August 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119204736/https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2017/jason-lowe-signs-for-blues/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後作客[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]的比賽首次先發上場。這場比賽另有五人也是首次代青球會上場<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/41132799 |title=Norwich City 1–0 Birmingham City |publisher=BBC Sport |date=9 September 2017 |accessdate=10 September 2017 |archive-date=2017-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911074337/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/41132799 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-player-ratings-how-13596902 |title=Birmingham City player ratings: How we rated the new look Blues against Norwich City |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=9 September 2017 |accessdate=10 September 2017 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910125647/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-player-ratings-how-13596902 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月中他再度受傷。他在伯明翰期間只上場11次，季末被釋出<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44171575 |title=Birmingham City: Midfielders Jason Lowe and Andrew Shinnie released |publisher=BBC Sport |date=18 May 2018 |accessdate=18 May 2018 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804114011/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44171575 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===博爾頓===
離開伯明翰城後，他與[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]簽下兩年合約，為球會新球季首簽成員<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bwfc.co.uk/news/2018/june/jason-lowe-joins-bolton-wanderers/ |title=Jason Lowe joins Bolton Wanderers |first=Theo |last=Squires |publisher=Bolton Wanderers F.C. |date=8 June 2018 |accessdate=9 June 2018 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226160557/https://www.bwfc.co.uk/news/2018/june/jason-lowe-joins-bolton-wanderers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44415871 |title=Jason Lowe: Bolton Wanderers sign midfielder on two-year deal |publisher=BBC Sport |date=8 June 2018 |accessdate=8 June 2018 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626125906/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44415871 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
賈森·洛曾入選英格蘭[[歐洲U-19足球錦標賽|歐洲U-19足球錦標賽]]參賽名單，但最終因傷而未能成事<ref name=wc>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefa.com/England/mens-u20s/News/2011/lowe-world-cup-110811|title=Lowe's World Cup reflections|author=Nicholas Veevers|date=12 August 2011|publisher=The FA|accessdate=28 October 2011|archive-date=2013-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123100511/http://www.thefa.com/England/mens-u20s/News/2011/lowe-world-cup-110811|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lowe forced out for England|url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/8271951.Lowe_forced_out_for_England/|publisher=The Lancashire Telegraph|date=14 July 2010|accessdate=10 June 2017|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613160834/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/8271951.Lowe_forced_out_for_England/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年2月9日英格蘭U20對法國U20是他首次代表國家青年隊<ref name=wc/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/mens-u20s/News/match-centre/2011/England%20v%20France/england-france-090211 |title=VIDEO: U20s sunk in Shrewsbury |author=Matt Phillips |date=9 February 2011 |publisher=The FA |accessdate=28 October 2011 |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104230023/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u20s/news/match-centre/2011/england%20v%20france/england-france-090211 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Jason Lowe profile">{{cite news|url=http://www.rovers.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10303~54649,00.html|publisher=Blackburn Rovers FC|title=Jason Lowe profile|accessdate=30 March 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110321172222/http://www.rovers.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10303~54649,00.html|archivedate=2011-03-21}}</ref>。2011年7月，他入選[[國際足協U-20世界盃|國際足協U-20世界盃]]參賽名單，以隊長身份領軍上場，最終在16強被淘汰出局<ref name=wc/><ref>{{cite news|title=Blackburn Rovers duo in the England U20 squad|url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/9185230.Blackburn_Rovers_duo_in_U20_squad/|publisher=The Lancashire Telegraph|date=9 August 2011|accessdate=10 June 2017|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613160935/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/9185230.Blackburn_Rovers_duo_in_U20_squad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年11月，他被提升至[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]，並在[[2013年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2013年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]資格賽對[[挪威21歲以下國家足球隊|挪威U21]]比賽中上場並以2-1取勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15251376.stm|title=Norway U21 1–2 England U21|date=10 October 2011|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=28 October 2011|archive-date=2011-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013120251/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15251376.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年5月，他入選參加歐洲U21足球錦標賽名單，赴[[以色列|以色列]]參賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2013/may/lowe-gets-england-call/|title=Lowe gets England call|publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C.|date=14 May 2013|accessdate=10 June 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610160204/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2013/may/lowe-gets-england-call/|archivedate=2017-06-10|deadurl=no}}</ref>。這項賽事他共上場2次，而英格蘭U21亦在小組賽出局，這亦是他最後一次代表英格蘭青年隊<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2013/june/england-crash-out/|title=England Crash Out of the Tournament|publisher=Blackburn Rovers F.C.|date=10 June 2013|accessdate=10 June 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610161058/https://www.rovers.co.uk/news/2013/june/england-crash-out/|archivedate=2017-06-10|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

